videos.headline: Clifford connects with Hamler for 23-yard Penn State TD
videos.description: KJ Hamler beats his defender and QB Sean Clifford finds him in the end zone for a 23-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Clifford connects with Hamler for 23-yard Penn State TD) 2019/10/5

videos.headline: Clifford finds the open gap for a TD
videos.description: Penn State QB Sean Clifford runs in a 3-yard touchdown for a 14-0 lead over Purdue.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One Play (Clifford finds the open gap for a TD) 19/10/05

videos.headline: Penn State burns Purdue with 72-yard TD
videos.description: Sean Clifford finds Jahan Dotson over the middle and Dotson burns the Purdue defense for a 72-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Penn State burns Purdue with 72-yard TD) 2019/10/05

videos.headline: Clifford connects with Freiermuth for a TD
videos.description: Sean Clifford lobs a short 7-yard pass to Pat Freiermuth for Penn State's third touchdown of the first half.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One Play (Clifford connects with Freiermuth for a TD) 19/10/05

videos.headline: Plummer finds Anderson for Purdue's 1st TD
videos.description: Jack Plummer throws to well defended Amad Anderson Jr. for a 15-yard touchdown, which puts the Boilermakers on the board.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One Play (Plummer finds Anderson for Purdue's 1st TD) 19/10/05
